        Returns the number of lines created. If the number of lines to be created exceeds the given maxLines, compress the extraneous lines into a single line. See also #renderLinesWithMaybeTruncation.
        Parameters:
        renderer - the renderer to use for rendering lines
        lines - the builder to add the rendered lines to
        maxLines - the maximum number of lines to render
        alwaysSortByTime - true if the rendered lines should be sorted by time
